Package: templr
Type: Package
Title: MASCOTNUM Algorithms Template Tools
Version: 0.1-0
Date: 2022-08-05
Author: Yann Richet <yann.richet@irsn.fr>
Maintainer: Yann Richet <yann.richet@irsn.fr>
Description: Helper functions for MASCOTNUM algorithm template, for design of numerical expriment practice:
    \begin{itemize}
      \item algorithm template parser to support MASCOTNUM specification <https://www.gdr-mascotnum.fr/template.html>,
      \item ask & tell decoupling injection (inspired by Gilles Pujol <https://search.r-project.org/CRAN/refmans/sensitivity/html/decoupling.html>) 
          to use "crimped" algorithms (like uniroot, optim, ...) outside R,
      \item basic template examples: Brent algorithm for 1 dim root finding, L-BFGS-B from optim.
    \end{itemize}
License: Apache License (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
Depends: R (>= 4.0)
Imports: utils, stats, remotes
Suggests: testthat, future
URL: https://github.com/MASCOTNUM/templr
